descriptionShort: A social app designed to help you make friends worldwide.
title: Yepop: discover the world

creator: Yepop Team
descriptionHtml:
Yepop is here for you if you want to meet the world without leaving your house!

Check out our key features below:

⭐Discover & Chat
Whether you are interested in a foreign culture or looking for someone to practice your foreign language skills, Yepop is what you need. Not only can you come across interesting souls around the world, but you can chat and become friends with them!

⭐Fun & cute filters
Need an ice-breaker? Check out our live stickers and filters ✨✨. Make a funny face and have a good laugh with your new friends, or apply a dazzling effect to make an impression. We’re sure you’ll have tons of fun with them.

⭐Establish friendship & stay in touch
Chatting with someone beyond your daily social circle can be the first step to a life-long friendship. If you really hit it off with someone, you can add them to your friend list. And no need to worry about losing memorable moments of your friendship, cuz you can always come back and check them in your private chat history.

⭐No language barrier
Automatic translation lets online communication ignite sparks beyond the language barrier. You can make international friends and share about your cultures worry-free, as your messages are translated instantly.


Remember to be polite and respectful, and you’re ready to go. Have fun! 😄👍
